snippet.title: Super Mario 3D World - Full Game (All Green Stars & Stamps)
snippet.description:
A 100% Complete Walkthrough of Super Mario 3D World for the Nintendo Wii U. This is an instructional video that shows the viewer how to complete the entire game by showing off all 12 Worlds, all Green Stars, all Stamps and all Captain Toad Levels.

Subscribe to NintendoCentral: ► https://www.youtube.com/c/NintendoCentral

Super Mario 3D World Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLJY2r98E0ngJ0f6m7IZd1zO3FvnG_DU59

My videos are edited to be straight to the point with my creative input. All gameplay is my own and recorded and edited by me.
